### 1. Health Check (Verificación de Conexión SQLite)
GET http://localhost:8001/health
Accept: application/json

###

### 2. Listar Clientes (Paginación por defecto: Página 1, 10 registros)
GET http://localhost:8001/customers
Accept: application/json

###

### 3. Listar Clientes con Paginación personalizada (Página 1, 5 registros)
GET http://localhost:8001/customers?page=1&per_page=5
Accept: application/json

###

### 4. Filtrar Clientes por Nombre de Empresa (Busca "Alfreds")
GET http://localhost:8001/customers?name_filter=Alfreds
Accept: application/json

###

### 5. Listar Clientes Ordenados por Nombre de Empresa (Orden Descendente)
GET http://localhost:8001/customers?sort_field=companyName&sort_order=desc&per_page=5
Accept: application/json

###

### 6. Obtener un Cliente Específico por ID (ALFKI)
GET http://localhost:8001/customers/ALFKI
Accept: application/json

###

### 7. Crear un Nuevo Cliente (ID: CODEX, CodeCrypto Academy)
POST http://localhost:8001/customers
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customerId": "CODEX",
  "companyName": "CodeCrypto Academy",
  "contactName": "José Viejó",
  "contactTitle": "Instructor Rust",
  "address": "Calle Falsa 123",
  "city": "Madrid",
  "region": "MD",
  "postalCode": "28001",
  "country": "España",
  "phone": "+34 123 456 789",
  "fax": null
}

###

### 8. Obtener el Cliente Creado para verificar (CODEX)
GET http://localhost:8001/customers/CODEX
Accept: application/json

###

### 9. Actualizar los Datos del Cliente Creado (Cambiar teléfono y contacto)
PUT http://localhost:8001/customers/CODEX
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customerId": "CODEX",
  "companyName": "CodeCrypto Academy S.L.",
  "contactName": "Juan Carlos Pérez",
  "contactTitle": "Lead Engineer Rust",
  "address": "Calle Falsa 123",
  "city": "Madrid",
  "region": "MD",
  "postalCode": "28001",
  "country": "España",
  "phone": "+34 999 999 999",
  "fax": null
}

###

### 10. Eliminar el Cliente de Prueba (CODEX)
DELETE http://localhost:8001/customers/CODEX
Accept: application/json

###

### 11. Intentar obtener el Cliente Eliminado (Debe retornar 404 Not Found)
GET http://localhost:8001/customers/CODEX
Accept: application/json
